content:
ITelemetryInitializer Interface

Definition

Represents an object that initializes ITelemetry objects.

In this Article

public interface ITelemetryInitializer

Remarks

The instances use objects to automatically initialize properties of the objects.

Methods

Initialize(ITelemetry)

Initializes properties of the specified ITelemetry object.
